.BURGLARY.1800.2403.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-news.now.com%2Fnewsimage%2FNewsImage%2FKLE.BURGLARY.1800.2403.jpg&h=a4bb80dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://hkpic.crntt.com/upload/201201/30/101993997.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkpic.crntt.com%2Fupload%2F201201%2F30%2F101993997.jpg&h=79908243&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上門派傳單就係公眾地方內擾亂秩序行為 咁呢幾個拉咗未啊?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de855e5259fc3c81bc47c8626b4a7444367888cd","tid":1805144,"uid":125026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T05:22:25.000Z","msg":"呢啲真係中國人民志願軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e888df7477b86093c4329f6c60390e802f28018","tid":1805144,"uid":2994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T05:25:03.000Z","msg":"好勇"}]}